description:
This is a 27 minute workout called '25 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT || Energising Mat Pilates' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
